---

<main
  class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 place-items-center pt-16 pb-8 md:pt-12 md:pb-24">
  <div class="py-6 md:order-1 block">
    <Picture
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Communication Link Logo"
      widths={[200, 400, 600]}
      sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 620px"
      loading="eager"
      format="avif"
    />
  </div>
  <div>
    <h1
      class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-bold lg:tracking-tight xl:tracking-tighter">
      Empowering Communication for All
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-500 lg:text-xl dark:text-gray-400">
      Bridging the Gap Between Deaf and Hearing Communities
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mt-4 text-slate-600 max-w-xl">
      At Communication Link we provide American Sign Language Interpreting services to ensure that everyone has the ability to connect with each other and be understood, in the least restrictive way posssible. Together, let's create a more inclusive world.
